to my office--

498
00:23:33,959 --> 00:23:36,041
Short, quick answers.
Please.

499
00:23:36,083 --> 00:23:39,041
Okay.
Well, a-a few months ago,

500
00:23:39,083 --> 00:23:42,041
you found out that your mother
