531
00:25:03,667 --> 00:25:05,625
Have a seat.

532
00:25:05,667 --> 00:25:07,625
Please.
I'm glad you came back.

533
00:25:07,667 --> 00:25:10,166
Uh...

534
00:25:10,208 --> 00:25:12,625
I'm sorry if yesterday,

535
00:25:12,667 --> 00:25:16,333
you felt, um... pushed.

