560
00:26:18,625 --> 00:26:20,792
But I'm there every day.

561
00:26:20,834 --> 00:26:22,166
Mm-hmm.

562
00:26:22,208 --> 00:26:26,667
And I'm afraid
that Dr. Wallace may be right.

563
00:26:29,709 --> 00:26:32,041
