um, persistent.

576
00:27:05,083 --> 00:27:07,000
Well, good. Good.

577
00:27:07,041 --> 00:27:09,542
I'll see you later.
Okay.

578
00:27:09,583 --> 00:27:11,917
Dr. Wilder.

579
00:27:15,583 --> 00:27:17,583
You like him.

580
00:27:17,625 --> 00:27:20,792
William? Yeah.
